top_projects.description: This repository contains the code for a computer vision-based air hockey game developed using OpenCV and Python. The game is designed to be played using a webcam or other camera device, with the computer vision algorithm tracking the movement of the puck and paddles.

top_projects.name: PACMAN-AI-Micro-Project
top_projects.description: This project is a recreation of the classic Pac-Man game, built using Pygame, a popular library for developing 2D games in Python. The project was developed as part of an AI Micro Project, focusing on implementing game mechanics, pathfinding algorithms for ghost AI, and a smooth, user-friendly experience.
